# Frontend Rules for Web App

## Custom Components

Custom application components (like `Header.tsx`) should be placed directly in `src/components/`:

```typescript
import Header from "@/components/Header";
```

## shadcn/ui Components

Use shadcn/ui components from [https://ui.shadcn.com/docs/components](https://ui.shadcn.com/docs/components) for UI primitives.

### Adding Components

To add a new shadcn component, run this command from the `apps/web` folder:

```bash
cd apps/web
bunx --bun shadcn@latest add {{component}}
```

Replace `{{component}}` with the component name (e.g., `button`, `card`, `dialog`, `input`, etc.).

